<p>The post <a href="https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/your-abdominal-core-expert-shares-tips-for-protecting-a-part-of-the-body-you-may-not-think-about/">Your abdominal core: Expert shares tips for protecting a part of the body you may not think about&nbsp;&nbsp;</a> appeared first on <a href="https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org">Mayo Clinic News Network</a>.</p>
